<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bahkan tidak bisa menggengam tanganmu
atau menautkan lengan.</font>

741
01:03:28,990 --> 01:03:30,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Ditambah apa?</font>

742
01:03:30,360 --> 01:03:33,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sangat pemalu, seolah kita belum pernah ciuman sebelumnya.</font>

743
01:03:36,560 --> 01:03:39,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingin ciuman?</font>

744
01:03:39,520 --> 01:03:42,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Um... bagaimana bisa kau bertanya langsung begitu?</font>

745
01:03:42,790 --> 01:03:46,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan menciumku kalau aku bilang mau?</font>

746
01:03:48,890 --> 01:03:51,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bahkan tidak bisa melakukannya tadi saat lampu dimatikan
dan suasananya mendukung.</font>

747
01:04:46,620 --> 01:04:49,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Apaan itu? Hanya pelukan?</font>

748
01:05:08,560 --> 01:05:09,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu bukan...</font>

749
01:05:10,690 --> 01:05:13,090
<font color=#FFFF00>...hadiah Valentine.</font>

750
01:05:13,190 --> 01:05:14,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

751
01:05:15,320 --> 01:05:17,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku memberinya tanpa alasan tertentu.</font>

752
01:05:20,160 --> 01:05:21,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Um, kalau begitu...</font>

753
01:05:25,860 --> 01:05:26,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pergi.</font>

754
01:05:28,290 --> 01:05:29,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Um...</font>

755
01:05:35,760 --> 01:05:36,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu.</font>

756
01:05:41,560 --> 01:05:42,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Bos.</font>

757
01:06:02,260 --> 01:06:03,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu...</font>

758
01:06:04,090 --> 01:06:05,520
<font color=#FFFF00>...hadiah Valentine dariku...</font>

759
01:06:07,220 --> 01:06:08,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...untukmu.</font>

760
01:06:42,630 --> 01:06:43,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Eun Hwan Gi <i>Daepyonim.</i></font>

761
01:06:45,990 --> 01:06:47,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar, 'kan?</font>

762
01:06:48,160 --> 01:06:49,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Um, iya.</font>

763
01:06:50,720 --> 01:06:51,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa kau?</font>

764
01:06:52,290 --> 01:06:53,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Malang sekali.</font>

765
01:06:54,760 --> 01:06:55,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tersenyum bahagia...</font>

766
01:06:57,160 --> 01:06:59,190
<font color=#FFFF00>...di samping Ro Woon.</font>

767
01:07:00,690 --> 01:07:01,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Padahal kau tidak berhak.</font>

